<lyrics>[V1]
 1- lmạ ạ̉kwn tʿbạn .. ạ̉rwḥ lmyn gẖyrk
 ạ̹nt ạlly tryḥny yạ yswʿ .. (ạ̉rkʿ wạ̉ṣly lk)2
 2- lmạ ạ̉kwn gẖlṭạn .. ạ̉rwḥ lmyn gẖyrk
 ạ̹nt ạlly tsạmḥny yạ yswʿ .. (ạ̉rkʿ wạ̉ṣly lk)2
 3- lmạ ạ̉kwn mryḍ .. ạ̉rwḥ lmyn gẖyrk
 ạ̹nt ạlly tsẖfyny yạ yswʿ .. (ạ̉rkʿ wạ̉ṣly lk)2
 4- lmạ ạ̉kwn ḥzyn .. ạ̉rwḥ lmyn gẖyrk
 ạ̹nt ạlly tʿzyny yạ yswʿ .. (ạ̉rkʿ wạ̉ṣly lk)2
 5- lmạ ạ̉kwn mẓlwm .. ạ̉rwḥ lmyn gẖyrk
 ạ̹nt ạlly tnṣfny yạ yswʿ .. (ạ̉rkʿ wạ̉ṣly lk)2
 6- lmạ ạ̉kwn ḥyrạn .. ạ̉rwḥ lmyn gẖyrk
 ạ̹nt ạlly trsẖdny yạ yswʿ .. (ạ̉rkʿ wạ̉ṣly lk)2
 7- lmạ ạ̉kwn ʿṭsẖạn .. ạ̉rwḥ lmyn gẖyrk
 ạ̹nt ạlly trwyny yạ yswʿ .. (ạ̉rkʿ wạ̉ṣly lk)2
 8- lmạ ạ̉kwn fy ḍyq .. ạ̉rwḥ lmyn gẖyrk
 ạ̹nt ạlly tnqdẖny yạ yswʿ .. (ạ̉rkʿ wạ̉ṣly lk)2</lyrics>
<title>lmạ ạ̉kwn tʿbạn</title>
</song>